                <p>There isn't much here yet. Soon we will let you see your calendars, your friends, your mailbox, stuff you can edit, etc.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                Copyright &copy; 2015 Casey Marshall<br>
                Fork us so hard on <a href="https://github.com/csm/showgregator">github</a>.
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
